productDetails.name: Brava Soccer Youth Package Soccer Ball

Made for training, this soccer ball retains air well within its butyl bladder and offers a soft-touch cover with colorful graphics that's tough enough to withstand the rigors of training and is highly visible.

productDetails.imageAltDesc: Brava Soccer Kids' Soccer Shin Guards
productDetails.name: Brava Soccer Kids' Soccer Shin Guards
productDetails.longDescription: Play safe with the Brava Soccer Kids' Soccer Shin Guards. Thanks to the ankle guards and lightweight polyurethane shells, you'll be able to jump into the game with confidence knowing your ankles and shins are protected. The interiors are backed with soft EVA foam padding for comfort, and the elastic straps make it easy to find a secure fit.
productDetails.shortDescription: The Brava Soccer Kids' Soccer Shin Guards feature soft EVA foam padding and lightweight shells.
